{"tid":94863,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【證監出手】惠理兩隻基金違規 被罰400萬元","createTime":"2017-01-25T14:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T05:46:03.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e9b37686f0ff87f1f0158990405a8c6d7322670","tid":94863,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T14:05:22.000Z","msg":"【證監出手】惠理兩隻基金違規 被罰400萬元<br />\n<br />\n2017-01-25 17:47:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n惠理基金管理的兩隻證監會認可基金，違反監管規定，被證監會分別罰款200萬元及予以譴責。<br />\n<br />\n證監會發現，惠理中華新星基金（新星基金）及惠理大中華高收益債券基金（高收益債券基金），曾發行超出其《組織章程大綱及細則》所規定的註冊股本的股數，違反《單位信託及互惠基金守則》的規定。另外，惠理在違規遭揭發後六個月，才向證監匯報。證監認為有關事故嚴重，令人質疑已發行予該等基金的投資者之股份的有效性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56222497&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56222497%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170125&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=521f4231\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56222497%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170125&h=0e85397e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56222497&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170125</a>"},{"pid":"0f2d612af277bcb89fd04f8bdb6e612e0bd89990","tid":94863,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}